# Email-review audit directory
#
# Populated by the email-review-strategist orchestrator each run:
#
#   <YYYY-MM-DD>-report.md             Daily review report (polished)
#   <YYYY-MM-DD>-changelog.md          What auto-applied + rollback commands
#   <YYYY-MM-DD>-patches/              Per-finding unified diffs (one .patch each)
#   <YYYY-MM-DD>-council-ledger.md     Council vote per contested finding
#   <YYYY-MM-DD>-archived-findings.md  Findings cut at adjudication caps
#   <YYYY-MM-DD>-trace.jsonl           Per-tool-call trace
#   weekly-<ISO-week>-impact.md        Friday digest with trajectory
#   cron.log                           Wrapper stdout/stderr (append-mode)
#   launchd-stdout.log                 Raw launchd stdout
#   launchd-stderr.log                 Raw launchd stderr
